videos.headline: Galloway pushes pile for extra yardage
videos.description: UT-Martin's Ladarius Galloway pushes the pile down field for extra yardage and a first down.

videos.headline: Cook connects with Pilpott connect on 31-yard deep ball
videos.description:
UT-Martin's Troy Cook throws 31-yard pass to Christian Philpott to move the 
Skyhawks into the red zone.

videos.headline: Cook fakes handoff, goes untouched into endzone
videos.description: Troy Cook sprints into the endzone untouched giving UT-Martin an early 6-0 lead.

videos.headline: Martin's INT puts UT-Martin near the redzone
videos.description: Tae Martin intercepts a pass thrown by Shea Patterson and puts the Skyhawks inside the Ole Miss 25-yard line.

videos.headline: Patterson uncorks deep ball to Brown to put Rebels on board
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson hits A.J. Brown on a 58-yard touchdown to cut UT-Martin's lead.

videos.headline: Galloway breaks free for 59-yard run
videos.description: UT-Martin's Ladarius Galloway takes the handoff on third-and-short and scampers 59 yards to the 2-yard line.

videos.headline: Grayson punches ball in to extend UT-Martin's lead
videos.description: UT-Martin's Marquez Grayson gets the handoff from two yards out and scores a touchdown.

videos.headline: Lodge's 58-yard catch puts Ole Miss in red zone
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson throws a 58-yard pass to DaMarkus Lodge to move the Rebels inside the UT-Martin 20-yard line.

videos.headline: Pennamon's 42-yard catch has Ole Miss on doorstep
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson throws a 42 yard pass to D'Vaughn Pennamon and puts the Rebels on UT-Martin's two-yard line.

videos.headline: Brown's 2nd TD puts Ole Miss on top at halftime
videos.description: A.J. Brown catches his second touchdown of the day and gives Ole Miss the 17-16 halftime lead.

videos.headline: Ole Miss' Luke: 'We didn't play well in all three phases'
videos.description: Ole Miss head coach Matt Luke is disappointed with his team's efforts in the first half vs UT-Martin.

videos.headline: Patterson connects with Brown for 37-yard gain
videos.description: Shea  Patterson hits A.J. Brown for a 37 yard pass.

videos.headline: Wilkins pounds ball up middle for 1-yard TD
videos.description: Jordan Wilkins runs the ball up the middle for a 1 yard touchdown run in the third quarter.

videos.headline: Lodge makes tough catch on sideline for 20-yard gain
videos.description: DaMarkus Lodge makes the catch on the sideline and gets his foot down.

videos.headline: Patterson's 3rd TD pass widens Ole Miss' lead
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson throws a 16-yard pass to Jordan Wilkins to give Ole Miss a double-digit lead.

videos.headline: Patterson tosses fourth TD of day to blow game open
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson hits DaMarkus Lodge for a 28-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: UT-Martin's Moore toe taps sideline to make tough grab
videos.description: UT-Martin's WR Jaylon Moore makes a tough catch along the sideline for a 23-yard gain.

videos.headline: Galloway takes handoff into end zone for 4-yard TD.
videos.description: UT-Martin's Ladarius Galloway turns the corner and sprints into the end zone for a touchdown.

videos.headline: Patterson hits Metcalf for his 5th passing TD of game
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson lobs up a two-yard touchdown pass to D.K. Metcalf to build on the Ole Miss lead.

videos.headline: Ole Miss interception stalls UT-Martin drive
videos.description: UT-Martin's Troy Cook tosses one up and is intercepted by Javien Hamilton.

videos.headline: Ole Miss QB Patterson: 'Sky is the limit for us'
videos.description: Ole Miss QB Shea Patterson talks about his school-record performance and the offensive success overall.

videos.headline: How Ole Miss can still improve after come from behind win
videos.description: Mike Morgan and Barrett Jones discuss Ole Miss' 45-23 victory over UT-Martin.
